cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with interactive image segmentation, which is a computer vision problem, and proposes a novel method for determining object and background regions. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also utilizes machine learning techniques and proposes a hybrid segmentation method, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with image topology and indeterminacy measurement, which could make it relevant to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
